snippet: With Tottenham Hotspur vying for a top finish in the English Premier League and the United States about to begin the final stage of its bid for the World Cup, Clint Dempsey has not slowed down.
abstract: Profile of Tottenham Hotspur midfielder Clint Dempsey, whose club is vying for top finish in English Premier League; Dempsey also plays for United States national team, which is about to begin final stage of its bid for World Cup.
lead_paragraph: With Tottenham Hotspur vying for a top finish in the English Premier League and the United States about to begin the final stage of its bid for the World Cup, Clint Dempsey has not slowed down.

headline.seo: Playing for Tottenham and United States, Clint Dempsey Rarely Stands Still
headline.main: A Soccer Star Who Rarely Stands Still
headline.print_headline: A Soccer Star Who Rarely Stands Still
